Package GeneticAlgorithm

Class Diet

java.lang.Object
GeneticAlgorithm.Diet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Diet extends Object implements Serializable
An instantiation of this class represents a complete diet with all four meals (Breakfast, Snack, Lunch, and Dinner). When the user saves a diet as an editable file, an object of this class is saved.
Author:
kxg708

  • Field Details

    • breakfast

      public ArrayList<MealOption> breakfast

    • filename

      public String filename
      The name of the editable file. When a new diet is generated, the initial value for this variable is "undefined". it can modified once the user saves it as an editable file. The file name is also displayed in the title of the diet display window.

    • path

      public String path
      The path of the editable file. When a new diet is generated, the initial value for this variable is "undefined". it can modified once the user saves it as an editable file.
